<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7點就是煙火大會啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了能一直抬頭看煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經徹底鍛鍊過脖子了——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
你準備好了嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7點開始就是煙火大會啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得發出不輸給煙火聲響的<delay8 />
聲音來鼓舞自己才行！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />真是令人期待啊——！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有沒有做好準備啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7點開始<delay8 />就是煙火大會啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從早上開始就情緒高漲到最高點，<delay20 />
隨時都處於準備萬全的狀態喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好咧——！放馬過來——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做好心理準備了嗎！？<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會馬上就要開始囉？<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟糕——！<delay20 />感覺有點緊張起來了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />趁現在先去一趟廁所好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />差不多要開始啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了避免不小心錯過第一發煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從現在開始可別眨眼睛喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">煙火大會終於開始啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的肌肉<delay8 />在煙火的照耀下<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />可別看入迷了喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊——<delay8 />煙火大會結束啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我很努力地在數<delay8 />有幾發煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是在煙火不斷發射的途中，<delay8 />
我就搞不懂數到多少了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />真是厲害啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很感動喔——！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />一直張著嘴巴觀賞煙火，<delay8 />
途中嘴裡<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像跑進了什麼東西，
那可真是嚇到我了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />結束啦——！<delay40 />
總覺得天空突然變暗了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說現在本來就是晚上嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊——<delay8 />今年的煙火大會結束啦。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年我一定要數出<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底發射了幾發煙火！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的煙火大會也結束了啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我連眨眼<delay8 />都覺得可惜，<delay20 />
所以就一直盯著煙火看喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果我的眼睛<delay20 />
現在有夠不舒服的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道是不是因為<delay frames="30" />
這是今年最後一場煙火大會，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這規模感覺比之前還要大啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>